parameters: \PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]This must be the barrier generator! Alright, here I go!
It seems there are no traps in this area.

Hey there, missy! You're here for the barrier generator,
aren't you?
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]How did you know... I was coming here?

Heard it from Belial. Amy betrayed us and let you escape,
huh.

Seriously... This is why you can't trust women. Just stay
quiet and do as men say.

You said something like that before. But the difference in
strength between men and women is clear; it's only natural
for the weak to obey the strong, right?

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]It's true that girls might not be able to beat men in sheer
strength. But instead, we have the strength to nurture life!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]If you're so strong, why don't you use that strength to
protect girls!?

Hahahaha! What an amusing thing to say, missy. Why should I
use my power for something like that?
I use my power solely for my own satisfaction!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]That's a wrong way to use power!

Then prove it to me, show me this 'right way to use power'
of yours!

This is a magical weapon powered by spiritual energy that
we've created.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]Don't tell me... you've gathered the spiritual energy from
the kidnapped girls for this...

That's right, with this thing we can easily crush the
Guardians!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]For such a purpose... so many girls...

Missy, you'll be the test subject for this thing. Do your
best to give us some good data!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[6]*pant*... *pant*... That was tough, but somehow we managed.
Work properly, you piece of junk!!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[8]Oh my... He fell down... Well, if he's a Liberator, he's
probably not dead, I guess...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]Anyway, we need to break the barrier first.

Have you seen this defeat scene before? Would you like to
see it again?
You've come back for more, young lady?

No matter how many times you come, the result will be the
same. Come at me!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]We have to destroy the barrier generator!
